This is a modal window. Beginning of dialog window. Escape will cancel and close the window. End of dialog window. Mrs. Christianah Amoke Akindele, aged, 76, died on January 7, 2018, during a brief illness. She was a lay-preacher of Methodist Church Nigeria, Matron of Trinity Methodist Church Choir, Itesi, Abeokuta, Ogun State. There will be a wake-keep at Methodist Bishop’s Court, Asero, Abeokuta, on February 1, 2018, between 4 and 6p.m. Burial service and interment follow at Trinity Methodist Church, Itesi, Abeokuta, on February 2 at 11am. A reception will be held at Anglican Bishop’s Court, Onikolobo, Abeokuta. She is survived by husband, children, grandchildren, brothers, sisters, in-laws and other family members.